00:15:56.200 --> 00:15:58.740
no integration whatsoever.

00:15:58.740 --> 00:16:00.585
Maybe you have a
different example.

00:16:00.585 --> 00:16:01.380
AUDIENCE: But No.

00:16:01.380 --> 00:16:05.750
Still [INAUDIBLE] just
[INAUDIBLE] the government.

00:16:05.750 --> 00:16:09.440
So I wonder if the type
of contracts [INAUDIBLE]

00:16:09.440 --> 00:16:12.590
engage with the private
[INAUDIBLE] concessions.

00:16:12.590 --> 00:16:13.900
I mean, there is a difference.

00:16:13.900 --> 00:16:16.640
There is a myriad of
