00:23:33.183 --> 00:23:35.020
is part of the TFL.

00:23:35.020 --> 00:23:38.310
Because you could essentially
go around the entire city just

00:23:38.310 --> 00:23:40.090
in zone 2.

00:23:40.090 --> 00:23:41.757
But if you don't tap
in in the right way

00:23:41.757 --> 00:23:43.340
when you transfer
trains or something,

00:23:43.340 --> 00:23:45.220
it will think you went
into the city and out.

00:23:45.220 --> 00:23:47.710
It's a lot cheaper to go
