00:24:36.920 --> 00:24:37.420
OK.

00:24:37.420 --> 00:24:38.630
Another-- oh, Eli.

00:24:38.630 --> 00:24:40.820
AUDIENCE: So you said
that you really need

00:24:40.820 --> 00:24:42.653
a tap-in, tap-out system
