00:24:50.640 --> 00:24:53.850
So in Europe, you
have some symptoms,

00:24:53.850 --> 00:24:56.680
especially it happens
more intercity.

00:24:56.680 --> 00:25:02.140
So you buy a ticket between
this station and that station

00:25:02.140 --> 00:25:04.650
and you have a paper ticket.

00:25:04.650 --> 00:25:08.110
And you when you board you
