01:07:04.360 --> 01:07:06.485
GABRIEL SANCHEZ-MARTINEZ:
Again, you do validation.

01:07:06.485 --> 01:07:07.390
There are policies.

01:07:07.390 --> 01:07:10.019
That's what these
card companies do.

01:07:10.019 --> 01:07:10.810
They're good at it.

01:07:10.810 --> 01:07:13.690
There is insurance for fraud.

01:07:13.690 --> 01:07:17.240
So they-- yeah.

01:07:17.240 --> 01:07:17.870
Yeah.

